-- Wimbledon Tennis Profit Rises to Record $60.8 Million, LTA Says
-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 2012-12-13T11:57:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-13/wimbledon-tennis-profit-rises-to-record-60-8-million-lta-says.html
This year’s profit from the
Wimbledon tennis championships has jumped 7.1 percent to a
record 37.7 millions pounds ($60.8 million), Britain’s Lawn
Tennis Association said in its annual report.  Wimbledon, the world’s only grass-court Grand Slam event,
has seen its profit rise 47 percent since 2008.  To contact the reporter on this story:
